node.text:
While the past few months have been tough for us all, it’s important to remember there’s still good being done in our community. To highlight some of the amazing work being done in Miami, I paid a visit to @joshuasheart on behalf of @jiffylubeintl and Do More to learn all about how Mrs. Mona Lissa Emeran is using her vehicle to give back.
Do More celebrates people who are serving their community through use of their cars — twice a week, Mona Lissa collects fresh bread and pastries from local bakeries to add to Joshua’s Heart meal deliveries, in hopes of giving recipients a wholesome meal and sense of normalcy during these times. On behalf of Jiffy Lube, I was honored to recognize Mona Lissa’s efforts with a year’s worth of free vehicle maintenance services to keep her on the road and helping the community!
Take a look and see why she’s driving to do more, what inspired this amazing selfless act, and the difference it’s making in so many lives. To learn more about Do More or how you can get involved, click the link in my bio or visit JiffyLube.com/DoMore. #Drive2DoMore

node.title: Jiffy Lube International x Do More x Joshua’s Heart Foundation

node.text: I’ve always believed entrepreneurs have to play the long game. Since I started, I’ve been playing the long game. Instant gratification cannot build a legacy, and then you come to learn that the long game is really the shortcut.

node.text:
Our Vermont Cheddar Truffled Mac and Cheese… insanely delicious! If I happen to walk in the kitchen as they are preparing one, and a couple of pieces are left in the mixing bowl, I eat them. I can’t help myself, it’s good even cold. 

.
.

.
.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Adrianne Calvo in Bimini, The Bahamas with @chefadrianne, and @rwbimini. May be an image of text that says 'O Lenet wald BIMINI BAHAMAS RESORT .CASINO Chef A AU Adrianne Dark Dark, Dining'.

node.text: I can’t wait! August 13th-15th! We take Dark Dining to paradise! It’s going to be an awesome epicurean weekend full of fun!!! If you’re like me, and you love travel, adventure, and of course, great food and wine, hanging out with me @rwbimini for a weekend is a great idea 😉. I’ve curated an itinerary that gives you just the right amount of time to take your tastebuds for a ride, catch some sun, catch some waves, and catch a buzz 😜! Tickets in my linktree!

node.text:
A favorite from Rome… Carbonara…. made with egg, Pecorino, guanciale, and black pepper…  Armando al Pantheon is said to serve the best authentic Carbonara in Rome. Some have already said Forte by Chef Adrianne, serves the best one this side of the Atlantic - and my heart couldn’t be happier!!!

.
.
.
.
.
.
.
#fortebychefadrianne #maximumflavor #miami #italian #pasta #foodie #instagood #photooftheday #igers #igdaily #zagat #buzzfeast #chefsofinstagram #foodnetwork

node.text: I had a great time learning about the beautiful island of Nevis and how it’s home to over 40 kinds of Mangoes! Speaking of mangoes, I added some ancho chili powder to my mango relish to add another dimension of flavor! Insanely delicious! @nevisnaturally
